[32m+[m[32m## Architecture overview[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe system is a **monorepo** with three runtime processes locally, and **two hosted services** in production (Vercel + Render/Railway).[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```mermaid[m
[32m+[m[32mflowchart TB[m
[32m+[m[32m    subgraph Client["Browser"][m
[32m+[m[32m        UI["ViZ Triage UI<br/>(Next.js 16)"][m
[32m+[m[32m    end[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m    subgraph Vercel["Vercel — frontend"][m
[32m+[m[32m        Next["Next.js App Router"][m
[32m+[m[32m        Proxy["/api/* rewrite proxy"][m
[32m+[m[32m    end[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m    subgraph Backend["Render / Railway — backend"][m
[32m+[m[32m        API["FastAPI + Uvicorn"][m
[32m+[m[32m        Graph["LangGraph runner"][m
[32m+[m[32m        Auth["Auth layer<br/>none | api_key | clerk"][m
[32m+[m[32m    end[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m    subgraph Data["Data & external services"][m
[32m+[m[32m        Neon["Neon PostgreSQL"][m
[32m+[m[32m        Claude["Anthropic Claude"][m
[32m+[m[32m        Search["Search provider<br/>DuckDuckGo | Tavily | MCP"][m
[32m+[m[32m        MCP["MCP server<br/>(optional, separate process)"][m
[32m+[m[32m        Clerk["Clerk JWT / JWKS"][m
[32m+[m[32m    end[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m    UI --> Next[m
[32m+[m[32m    Next --> Proxy[m
[32m+[m[32m    Proxy -->|"API_BACKEND_URL"| API[m
[32m+[m[32m    API --> Auth[m
[32m+[m[32m    Auth --> Graph[m
[32m+[m[32m    Graph --> Claude[m
[32m+[m[32m    Graph --> Search[m
[32m+[m[32m    Search -.->|"SEARCH_PROVIDER=mcp"| MCP[m
[32m+[m[32m    API --> Neon[m
[32m+[m[32m    Auth -.->|"AUTH_MODE=clerk"| Clerk[m
[32m+[m[32m    UI -.->|"optional sign-in"| Clerk[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m| Layer | Technology | Host |[m
[32m+[m[32m|-------|------------|------|[m
[32m+[m[32m| **UI** | Next.js 16, React 19, Tailwind 4, Framer Motion | **Vercel** |[m
[32m+[m[32m| **API** | FastAPI, LangGraph, Pydantic v2 | **Render / Railway / Fly.io** |[m
[32m+[m[32m| **Database** | PostgreSQL via SQLAlchemy async (`asyncpg`) | **Neon** (recommended) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| **LLM** | Claude Sonnet (default) | Anthropic API |[m
[32m+[m[32m| **Search** | DuckDuckGo, Tavily, or MCP | In-process or separate MCP server |[m
[32m+[m[32m| **Auth** | Clerk JWT (optional) | Clerk + FastAPI JWKS verification |[m
